llows blankets massagers and personal hair nail and bath and body products  xpresspa has over  employees including talented teams of professionally licensed massage therapists cosmetologists and nail technicians who are committed to providing exceptional customer experiencesform holdings entered into a definitive agreement to acquire  of xpresspa on august   on november   form holdings stockholders approved the acquisition and on december   the transaction closedto learn more about xpresspa visit wwwxpresspacom group mobile is a marketleading supplier of builttoorder rugged computers mobile devices and accessories group mobile provides a high touch sales experience with full service technical and customer support in the  billion dollar plus rugged mobile computer market group mobile offers thousands of products including rugged laptops rugged mobile handhelds rugged tablets rugged accessories and is an authorized retailer of more brands than any other rugged retailer these brands include panasonic getac xplore motion trimble gammatech and several others  form holdings acquired a  ownership of group mobile in october  to learn more about group mobile visit wwwgroupmobilecom fli charge is a wirefree power company dedicated to making it easier for people to power and charge the multitude of mobile electronic devices they use on a daily basis our goal is to lessen the burden of using electronic devices by eliminating the need to search andor fight for outlets and to carry power accessories everywhere fli charge designs develops manufactures and markets wirefree conductive power and charging solutions fli charge’s patented technology is the only wirefree power solution that is fully interoperable between different mobile devices ranging from smartphones to power tools and many more fli charge’s wirefree power solution can simultaneously power multiple devices on the same pad no matter their power requirements or positions on the pad fli charge’s conductive technology is the most efficient wirefree power solution and can be adapted to work with virtually all batterypowered devices on the market fli charge’s products are easily integrated into your everyday life and are safe and simple to use form holdings acquired a  ownership of fli charge in october  and acquired the remaining  in december  form holdings currently owns  of fli charge to learn more about fli charge visit wwwflichargecom infomedia is a privately owned united kingdom based leading provider of customer relationship management and monetization technologies to mobile carriers and device manufacturers in february  infomedia acquired the vringo mobile social application suite from form holdings in exchange for  ownership of infomedia to learn more about infomedia wwwinfomediaservicescouk the intellectual property division is engaged in the innovation development and monetization of intellectual property our portfolio consists of patents and patent applications covering telecom infrastructure remote monitoring internet search adinsertion wireless charging and mobile technologiesto download a list of our patents click hereto download a list of our standard essential patents and etsi declarations click here   all rights reserved form holdings corp       privacy policy     terms of use portfolio rss feedsir contactfinancial tear sheetinvestor presentation operating units team news investors contact us portfolio xpresspagroup mobilefli chargeinfomediaintellectual property xpresspa is the industryleading luxury travel spa business serving almost  million air travelers each year at its  locations across  major airportsxpresspa is the industryleading luxury travel spa business serving almost  million air travelers each year at its  locations across  major airports including licensed locations in amsterdam’s schiphol and dubai’s international airports  xpresspa offers travelers premium spa services including massages reflexology stress and tension release manicures pedicures facia