anies with superior growth potential  forms current holdings include xpresspa group mobile fli charge infomedia and intellectual property assets  xpresspa is the worlds largest airport spa company group mobile is a provider of rugged mobile and fielduse computing products serving customers worldwide  fli charge designs develops licenses manufactures and markets wireless conductive power and charging solutions  infomedia is a leading provider of customer relationship management and monetization technologies to mobile carriers and device manufacturers  form holdings intellectual property division is engaged in the development and monetization of intellectual property to learn more about form holdings corp visit wwwformholdingscom   contactsform holdingsjeff sonnekicrjeffsonnekicrinccom advertising partners  thestreet inc all rights reservedaction alerts plus is a registered trademark of thestreet inc compare brokers fh stock price  form holdings corp stock quote us nasdaq  marketwatch sections watchlist signup • login search bulletin us europe asia fx rates futures range d d m m m y y dow    sp     nasdaq    globaldow    gold    oil    sp  movers algn  mhk  expe  col  fls  sbux  mo  gt  latest newsall times eastern p who are the beneficiaries of a k if my wife and i die at the same time p charlie gard british baby at center of controversy has died p under armours stocks low price doesnt mean it is cheap p retirement weekly news and analysis p floyd mayweather says he is going to make bank off an ico p updated foxconn’s history of broken promises casts a shadow on wisconsin news p goodyear stock stumbles  after quarter ‘played out differently than we expected’ p updated this city’s subway system will soon run mostly on renewable energy p updated which state’s  plan is right for you p updated why so many teens are clueless about money to be replaced home investing quotes stocks united states fh overview compare quotes stock screener earnings calendar sectors nasdaq fh u